00:37.204 --> 00:42.290
Our subject is: "The death penalty".

00:44.795 --> 00:49.210
Which of these substances is used for the lethal medication mix -

00:50.259 --> 00:54.970
- that will cause death within five to ten minutes ?

00:55.764 --> 01:02.557
A: Ringer's lactate 
B: Cefuroxime.

01:03.313 --> 01:10.152
C: Pentothal. 
D: Sodium chloride.

01:11.613 --> 01:16.199
Take your time, Emily.

01:21.999 --> 01:24.898
Wow, she really hit the jackpot tonight didn’t she?

01:24.918 --> 01:25.983
Yep.

01:26.003 --> 01:29.371
