You too Sir.

08:50.613 --> 08:51.820
Welcome.

08:55.326 --> 08:59.366
You all know the rules, right?
You choose the subject and then we .....

09:03.084 --> 09:05.622
You have three minutes to answer the question.

09:06.129 --> 09:10.669
Three minutes that can change your life

09:31.613 --> 09:33.650
You one of the new owners?

09:46.044 --> 09:47.706
