15:29.846 --> 15:32.759
Who are you? 
Why did you tie me up?

15:34.267 --> 15:35.383
Answer!

15:35.560 --> 15:37.893
What the Hell is going on here?

15:38.855 --> 15:41.017
May I remind you, that an unanswered question -

15:41.190 --> 15:45.605
- is the same as a wrong answer.

15:50.032 --> 15:51.739
Now answer.

15:52.326 --> 15:56.070
What’s the question again?

15:57.248 --> 16:02.150
Am I - A: Unemployed?
B: A sales manager?

16:02.170 --> 16:05.584
C: A teacher? 
D: A hooker?

16:08.676 --> 16:12.966
I don’t know.
You don’t look unemployed.

16:15.099 --> 16:19.292
