it was obviously a waste of time.

18:56.093 --> 18:59.507
Yes. I remember.

19:41.305 --> 19:42.671
You’re crazy.

19:54.276 --> 20:00.648
Do you remember it Jack?
It's really simple.

20:04.161 --> 20:07.074
Your teacher would have been disappointed 
if you had forgotten that, hmm

20:09.834 --> 20:11.370
Can you sing it?

20:13.045 --> 20:14.536
Sing it.

20:16.674 --> 20:18.210
Sing.

20:18.759 --> 20:21.752
Show me that your teacher didn’t waste her time on you.

21:01.594 --> 21:05.508
That was very good. Very good.

21:11.228 --> 21:12.594
Let’s get on with the game.

21:14.648 --> 21:17.857
We’re going to play for your toenail.

21:20.613 --> 21:23.947
Question number 2, 
a movie question.

21:26.744 --> 21:30.829
Which is the odd movie out?

21:31.373 --> 21:34.866
A: Misery?

21:36.128 --> 21:42.500
