Those are the rules of the game.

22:30.641 --> 22:32.633
This is not a game.

22:46.907 --> 22:48.193
Answer!

22:48.742 --> 22:50.734
I have no idea.
Answer!

22:52.079 --> 22:53.035
Damn shit!

23:03.966 --> 23:07.425
Oh my God! No...

23:08.220 --> 23:14.057
No, no... Oh my God...

23:15.769 --> 23:17.351
No!

23:20.024 --> 23:21.515
That’s what happens. See?

23:22.526 --> 23:23.812
Oh my God.

23:28.616 --> 23:30.681
I hope this will make you consider -

23:30.701 --> 23:33.068
the consequences of the questions.

23:35.331 --> 23:38.119
Now, I’m going to ask the question again –

23:39.376 --> 23:44.292
- and we are going to play for the nail,
of your other big toe.

23:47.801 --> 23:52.216
Question # 2: 
Which is the odd movie out?

23:52.890 --> 23:58.978
Is it A: Misery 
B: Diabolique

23:59.980 --> 24:05.647
C: Kill Bill 
or D: Million Dollar Baby?

