24:18.123 --> 24:19.534
Either way,

24:22.962 --> 24:24.874
you should realise.

24:31.470 --> 24:36.465
Come on, Jack. 
You certainly know the answer.

24:38.018 --> 24:43.104
I mean, a man with your knowledge of films.

24:44.525 --> 24:47.893
You have the biggest DVD collection I have ever seen.

24:49.863 --> 24:51.320
You’ve ever seen?

24:51.824 --> 24:56.865
Yeah sure, 
Oh, I will have to give you back "The Big Lebowsky".

24:57.621 --> 24:59.283
You were in my apartment?

25:01.417 --> 25:02.908
Answer!

25:03.460 --> 25:04.667
Wait!

25:05.963 --> 25:07.249
Okay.

25:10.509 --> 25:11.499
Okay.

25:15.431 --> 25:19.971
