are revenge dramas.

25:33.907 --> 25:38.652
"Million Dollar Baby" 
is a sports drama.

25:40.080 --> 25:41.662
That's interesting.

25:42.583 --> 25:50.583
But it’s not, not the genre, 
No. No.

25:55.220 --> 25:57.132
