26:16.158 --> 26:19.617
"Misery" and "Diabolique"
are too obvious.

26:20.454 --> 26:27.497
"Kill Bill" is a, maybe some sick joke
Directed at me –

26:27.669 --> 26:32.289
- but I still, 
I still don’t know what the fuck you want!

26:33.550 --> 26:35.633
