You would have done it by now, so...

26:45.229 --> 26:47.391
- maybe it’s about the money.

26:49.775 --> 26:51.311
Is it the money?

26:56.865 --> 26:59.152
It's "Million Dollar Baby".

27:01.161 --> 27:02.368
Yes.

27:13.173 --> 27:15.335
Is that your final answer?

27:15.968 --> 27:20.588
Yes! 
Yes, You bitch!

27:25.894 --> 27:29.683
