35:17.741 --> 35:19.653
I love her.

35:21.995 --> 35:23.657
Let’s send her a message.

35:24.748 --> 35:29.334
Keep up the good work.

35:30.170 --> 35:38.170
Oh, and no, you do not have a fat ass,

35:42.349 --> 35:43.931
